   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>On profile pages, there are some styling oddities: If you are logged-in, the
Info box's "edit" link is in an odd place. aldeka can come up with a longer list
of oddities.

Also, the default user profile image is not as wide as the box. Perhaps the box
should shrink, or the profile picture can change, or something else can change
so it doesn't look odd.

We should get those cleaned-up before shipping the redesign.

(This bug is about the redesign of the site that is occurring during 0.12.02.
You can see that redesign in process, temporarily, here:
<a href="http://gentle-robot-6466.herokuapp.com/">http://gentle-robot-6466.herokuapp.com/</a> )</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
